# Cursor retrieval/indexing ignore rules.
#
# Goal: prevent embeddings for generated/vendor/log/cache artifacts so usage
# doesn’t burn embedding large, irrelevant directories.

# Node / build artifacts
**/node_modules/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.svelte-kit/**
**/.vercel/**
**/.netlify/**
**/out/**
**/.output/**
**/coverage/**
**/.turbo/**
**/.next/**
**/.nuxt/**

# Tauri / Rust build outputs
**/src-tauri/target/**
**/src-tauri/gen/**
**/src-tauri/.tauri/**
**/.tauri/**

# IDE files
**/.vscode/**
**/.idea/**

# Git / metadata
**/.git/**

# Logs / caches / databases
**/logs/**
**/*.log
**/data/**
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3

# Cursor-specific heavyweight artifacts (plans can be large and noisy)
**/.cursor/plans/**
**/.cursor/debug*.log
**/.cursor/agent-transcripts/**

# Java/Kotlin build caches (helps if they were being indexed previously)
**/.m2/**
**/.gradle/**
